#: ../../talk/federation_index.rst:2
msgid "Federation"
msgstr "Cónaidhm"

#: ../../talk/federation_index.rst:4
msgid ""
"With the Federation feature, users can create conversations across different"
" federated Talk instances and use Talk features as if they were on the same "
"server."
msgstr ""
"Leis an ngné Cónaidhme, is féidir le húsáideoirí comhráite a chruthú trasna "
"cásanna cónaidhme éagsúla Talk agus gnéithe Talk a úsáid amhail is dá mba ar"
" an bhfreastalaí céanna a bheadh ​​siad."

#: ../../talk/federation_index.rst:6
msgid "This feature must be enabled by a system administrator."
msgstr "Ní mór do riarthóir córais an ghné seo a chumasú."

#: ../../talk/federation_index.rst:9
msgid "Sending an invitation"
msgstr "Cuireadh á sheoladh"

#: ../../talk/federation_index.rst:13
msgid ""
"The moderator of the conversation can send an invite to a participant on a "
"different server:"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir le modhnóir an chomhrá cuireadh a sheoladh chuig rannpháirtí ar "
"fhreastalaí difriúil:"

#: ../../talk/federation_index.rst:19
msgid "Accepting an invitation"
msgstr "Glacadh le cuireadh"

#: ../../talk/federation_index.rst:21
msgid ""
"When receiving a notification, the user will see a counter of pending "
"invites above the conversations list."
msgstr ""
"Nuair a fhaigheann an t-úsáideoir fógra, feicfidh sé/sí cuntar de chuirí atá"
" ar feitheamh os cionn an liosta comhráite."

#: ../../talk/federation_index.rst:26
msgid ""
"Upon clicking it, more information will be provided about the inviting "
"party, and the user can either accept or decline the invitation."
msgstr ""
"Nuair a chliceálann tú air, cuirfear tuilleadh eolais ar fáil faoin bpáirtí "
"a thug cuireadh, agus is féidir leis an úsáideoir glacadh leis an gcuireadh "
"nó é a dhiúltú."

#: ../../talk/federation_index.rst:31
msgid ""
"By accepting the invite, the conversation will appear in the list as any "
"other one."
msgstr ""
"Trí ghlacadh leis an gcuireadh, beidh an comhrá le feiceáil sa liosta mar "
"aon cheann eile."

#: ../../talk/federation_index.rst:36
msgid ""
"You can use it to chat with participants from other federated servers, join "
"calls, and use other available Talk features."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat é a úsáid chun comhrá a dhéanamh le rannpháirtithe ó "
"fhreastalaithe cónaidhme eile, glaonna a bheith páirteach, agus gnéithe eile"
" de chuid Talk atá ar fáil a úsáid."
